        <abstract> 
<p>Reference to description of <hi rend="italic">Begonia phyllomaniaca</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Thanks for the explicit account of Pangenesis. Thinks he now follows CD’s ideas but Pangenesis is very difficult and speculative.</p>
            <p>Oliver has lost his little girl.</p>
